ers.com/markets/asia/global-economy-asian-factories-show-tentative-signs-recovery-china-improves-2024-09-02/</guid></item><item><title>预计亏损 26 亿美元后，香港新世界发展股价暴跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/shares-hong-kongs-new-world-development-plunge-after-26-bln-loss-forecast-2024-09-02/</link><description>香港主要房地产开发商新世界发展公司 (New World Development) 预计截至 6 月份的财政年度净亏损高达 200 亿港元（合 26 亿美元），其股价暴跌 14%。</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Sep 2024 02:46:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/shares-hong-kongs-new-world-development-plunge-after-26-bln-loss-forecast-2024-09-02/</guid></item><item><title>总统表示，如果中国想要台湾，也应该从俄罗斯手中夺回土地</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/if-china-wants-taiwan-it-should-also-take-back-land-russia-president-says-2024-09-02/</link><description>台湾总统赖清德在接受台湾媒体采访时表示，如果中国对台湾的主张涉及领土完整，那么它也应该从俄罗斯收回19世纪中国最后一个王朝签署的土地。</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Sep 2024 02:24:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/if-china-wants-taiwan-it-should-also-take-back-land-russia-president-says-2024-09-02/</guid></item><item><title>亚洲足球周</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/week-asian-football-2024-09-02/</link><description>本周亚洲足球的谈话要点：</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Sep 2024 01:54:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/week-asian-football-2024-09-02/</guid></item><item><title>中国敦促欧盟在南海问题上“客观公正”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-urges-eu-be-objective-fair-south-china-sea-issue-2024-09-02/</link><description>在欧盟对周末发生的事件发表评论后，中国敦促欧盟在南海问题上“客观、公正”，谨慎言行。</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Sep 2024 01:13:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-urges-eu-be-objective-fair-south-china-sea-issue-2024-09-02/</guid></item><item><title>由于中国数据疲软以及欧佩克+供应增加的前景，油价扩大跌幅</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/oil-extends-losses-prospect-higher-opec-supply-2024-09-02/</link><description>由于预期 OPEC+ 产量将从 10 月开始增加，以及全球最大的两个石油消费国中国和美国需求疲软的迹象，引发了对未来消费增长的担忧，周一油价扩大跌幅。</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Sep 2024 00:31:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/oil-extends-losses-prospect-higher-opec-supply-2024-09-02/</guid></item><item><title>股票和货币变得谨慎成为就业问题的关键</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1pix-2024-09-02/</link><description>周一亚洲股市低迷，投资者准备迎接充满数据的一周，最终将公布美国就业报告，该报告可能决定本月预期的降息是常规降息还是大幅降息。</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Sep 2024 00:29:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1pix-2024-09-02/</guid></item><item><title>非生产力新力量：中国青年承认失业</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/new-unproductive-forces-chinese-youth-owning-their-unemployment-2024-09-01/</link><description>批评人士称，政府政策偏向狭隘的科学技术领域，让其他行业下滑，有可能导致一代受过教育的年轻人找不到工作。</description><pubDate>Sun, 01 Sep 2024 23:08:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/new-unproductive-forces-chinese-youth-owning-their-unemployment-2024-09-01/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：中国给全球“金发姑娘”前景蒙上阴影</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-09-01/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Sun, 01 Sep 2024 21:47:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-09-01/</guid></item><item><title>随着西方限制措施的临近，中国将向非洲领导人推销绿色技术出口</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/china-pitch-green-tech-exports-african-leaders-western-curbs-loom-2024-09-01/</link><description>他们想听听中国计划如何兑现 2021 年起尚未兑现的承诺。</description><pubDate>Sun, 01 Sep 2024 17:08:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/china-pitch-green-tech-exports-african-leaders-western-curbs-loom-2024-09-01/</guid></item><item><title>美国公开赛第七天</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/us-open-day-seven-2024-09-01/</link><descripti